CLAIM

Usage:  claim [target]

Claims the tile you're currently on for your empire. This can also be used
to claim vehicles.

To claim things inside the radius of one of your cities, try "city claim".

You can't claim land that's inside another empire's city radius while at war
with that empire.

Privileged immortals can claim land/vehicles for other empires by giving the
empire name as the last arg.

