"DIPLOMACY BATTLE" "FRIENDLY WAR" "BATTLE WAR" "OFFER BATTLE"

Usage:  diplomacy battle <empire>

An offer of 'battle' is similar to declaring war, but it has no 'war cost',
and the other side must agree to it (like most diplomatic offers). Like a
regular war, the battle will end on its own if either side is logged off after
the battle has been going on for more than an hour. You can also end it by
offering peace or a truce.

During a battle, you can attack all members of the other empire, can besiege
their buildings, and can steal from their storage buildings.

See also: DIPLOMACY, WAR
