ESTABLISH ESTABLISHED ESTABLISHING "NOT ESTABLISHED" "CITY DELAY"

A city is not fully "established" until 2 game days (60 minutes) after you
found it. In-city-only buildings and functions won't work during this period,
and it will show as (establishing) on your city list.

Administrators: Time can be configured with config city minutes_to_full_city.
The purpose of this delay is to prevent exploits created by temporarily using
a spare city point, such as allowing city teleportation or guard towers.

See also: CITY COMMAND
