Trade also allows you to store and retrieve your empire's items from the other
empire's buildings (if you also have permission to use that building, for
example due to an alliance or if it's a public building). These resources still
go to/from your own empire's storage.

Trade relations raise your exchange rate with the other empire by 25%.

