 - Bonus Experience: Empire members get +5 bonus experience each day.
 - Tunnels: The empire can use the 'tunnel' command.
 - Fast Prospect: Members of the empire can prospect much faster.
 - Fast Excavate: Members of the empire excavate much faster when in-city.
 - Hidden Progress: The empire's progress won't show on the /progress channel.
 - Workforce Prospecting: Workforce can prospect.

* some technologies only function on the same island as the building that
  provides them

